      <title>Typora+免费图床</title>
      <link href="2021/03/10/Typora-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/"/>
      <url>2021/03/10/Typora-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="配置">配置</h2><p>打开Typora，点击文件，点击偏好设置，点击图像，如下图所示</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fristalpha/alpha/BlogPic/20210310160024.png" alt="image-20210310160016975"></p><p>上床服务选择PicGo（app）</p><p>路径选择PicGo安装路径</p><p>然后点击验证图片上床选项，提示成功即可</p><h2 id="使用">使用</h2><p>以qq截图为例，如下,点击上传图片。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fristalpha/alpha/BlogPic/20210310160724.png" alt="image-20210310160720859"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fristalpha/alpha/BlogPic/20210310161000.png" alt="image-20210310160838766"></p><p>等待一会，看到url路径变为jsd的即可。</p>]]></content>
      
      
